 \"Wayde van Niekerk\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wayde_van_Niekerk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wayde_van_Niekerk\"}, {\"begin\": 1493, \"end\": 1501, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999999217835, \"rank\": 7.538244139261347e-11, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1546, \"end\": 1552, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Duchy_of_Nassau\", \"score\": 0.9992571150401252, \"rank\": 0.0007401816496152822, \"text\": \"Nassau\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Duchy_of_Nassau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Duchy_of_Nassau\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lyles took the baton from Kyree King and accelerated through the line in 37.40 seconds after slick early handovers by Courtney\\u00a0Lindsey and Kenneth\\u00a0Bednarek.\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1721, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1591, \"end\": 1601, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyree_King\", \"score\": 0.9999999741885407, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kyree King\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyree_King\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyree_King\"}, {\"begin\": 1683, \"end\": 1691, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Courtney_Love\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.550665950806152e-18, \"text\": \"Courtney\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Courtney_Love\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Courtney_Love\"}, {\"begin\": 1692, \"end\": 1699, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parts_of_Lindsey\", \"score\": 0.9564684718339203, \"rank\": 0.03567413098623539, \"text\": \"Lindsey\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/res